&lt;p&gt;Culture Amp is seeking a Director, Legal to join our Legal team, reporting to our General Counsel. This is a senior, hands-on role that sits at the intersection of commercial and product legal work, spanning complex global deals, product collaboration, and mentoring a talented legal team. You&#39;ll bring deep commercial expertise and the strategic instincts to navigate M&amp;amp;A, enterprise transactions, and a fast-moving SaaS environment, all while helping the business grow responsibly and at pace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity to operate with real breadth, working across commercial deals globally, partnering closely with Sales and Product, and shaping the legal capability of the team around you. Your involvement across the business isn&#39;t just encouraged, it&#39;s essential. You&#39;ll need to be comfortable working through complex problems, finding the best commercial outcome, and translating legal complexity into clear, actionable guidance for senior stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
