&lt;li&gt;Lead and support complex commercial deals globally, including enterprise customer and vendor contracts, and M&amp;amp;A transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with the Product team to provide legal guidance on product development, integrations, data governance, and new feature releases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work across both commercial and product legal matters, bringing a broad and pragmatic perspective to the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and develop other members of the Legal team, helping to build capability and raise the bar across the function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Sales, Security, Marketing, and other business teams to provide clear, commercially-minded legal advice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and advise on evolving legal and regulatory landscapes relevant to a global SaaS business, including privacy, data governance and AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
